<div class="dentro_contenidos" style="display: block;" id="pagina_1">
<p>In this test, students have to show that they can understand a series of spoken material such as everyday conversations, lectures, speeches, interviews, talks and radio broadcasts.</p>
<p><b>What</b> <b>’</b> <b>s the test like?</b></p>
<p>The listening test consists of <b>4 parts</b>. Time allowed: <b>40 minutes</b>. You will listen to every text twice.</p>
<p>As you have been practicing listening skills throughout the previous modules of the course, we will only add some tips here that will help you improve your level of achievement.</p>
